  "text": "Bmp15, gdf9, gdf3 and smad1/5/8 were XX-enriched genes from our transcriptome data. To ascertain which population of cells in gonads expressed these genes, ISH was performed using tilapia ovaries and testes at 180 dah. The fixation, embedding, sectioning of dissected gonads and ISH were performed as described previously [CITATION_1] . Probes of sense and antisense digoxigenin (DIG)-labeled RNA strands were transcribed in vitro from linearized pGEM-T easy-bmp15/gdf9/gdf3/smad1/smad5/smad8 cDNA using a RNA labeling kit (Roche, Mannheim, Germany).",
